{% extends "default.twig" %}
{% import "components.twig" as components %}

{% block title %}Ali Khorsandfard – Lernberater, Dozent, IT Expert{% endblock %}

{% block content %}
    <div class="bg-white bg-opacity-90 shadow-md rounded-lg p-10">
        <h1 class="text-4xl font-extrabold text-gray-800 mb-2">Jörg Feller</h1>
        <h2 class="text-xl text-blue-700 font-semibold mb-6">Lernberater · Dozent · IT Expert</h2>
        <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row gap-8 mb-8">
            <div class="flex-1">
                <p class="text-lg text-gray-700 mb-4">
                    Welcome to my personal website! I am passionate about lifelong learning, technology, and the beauty of both science and art. My career spans educational consulting, university lecturing, and advanced IT solutions.
                </p>
                <ul class="list-disc list-inside text-gray-700 mb-4">
                    <li><strong>Lernberater:</strong> Helping students and professionals unlock their full potential through modern learning strategies.</li>
                    <li><strong>Dozent:</strong> University lecturer in computer science, mathematics, and interdisciplinary innovation.</li>
                    <li><strong>IT Expert:</strong> Decades of experience in software development, system architecture, and digital transformation.</li>
                </ul>
            </div>
            <div class="flex-shrink-0 flex items-center justify-center">
                <img src="/assets/images/me.jpg" alt="Ali Khorsandfard" class="rounded-full w-40 h-40 object-cover border-4 border-blue-200 shadow-lg"/>
            </div>
        </div>
        <hr class="my-8">
        <div class="flex flex-col gap-6 mb-8">
            <div class="bg-white bg-opacity-80 rounded-xl shadow-md p-6 transition-transform duration-200 hover:-translate-y-1 hover:shadow-xl">
                <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-800 mb-2">Quantum Physics</h3>
                <p class="text-gray-700 mb-2">Quantum physics reveals a world where particles can be in two places at once, and information can travel faster than light. Did you know? The phenomenon of quantum entanglement was called "spooky action at a distance" by Einstein, and it’s now at the heart of quantum computing and cryptography.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="bg-white bg-opacity-80 rounded-xl shadow-md p-6 transition-transform duration-200 hover:-translate-y-1 hover:shadow-xl">
                <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-800 mb-2">Japanese Art</h3>
                <p class="text-gray-700 mb-2">Inspired by the elegance and minimalism of Japanese art, I integrate its principles into my work and life. From the fleeting beauty of sakura blossoms to the bold lines of sumi-e ink painting, Japanese aesthetics teach us to find harmony in simplicity and nature.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="bg-white bg-opacity-80 rounded-xl shadow-md p-6 transition-transform duration-200 hover:-translate-y-1 hover:shadow-xl">
                <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-800 mb-2">Robotics</h3>
                <p class="text-gray-700 mb-2">Robotics is where imagination meets engineering. I am fascinated by how robots are transforming industries, healthcare, and even our homes. My work explores the intersection of AI, automation, and human creativity.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
{% endblock %}